WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:09.000
Madrid-Adolfo Suarez Barajas Airport Terminal T4

00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:14.000
Hello

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:23.000
We are about to land in Madrid T4

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:32.300
The T4 consists of the satellite building and main building

00:00:32.300 --> 00:00:41.500
These are connected by an automatic train

00:00:41.500 --> 00:00:51.000
The trains run every 2-3 minutes

00:00:51.000 --> 00:01:00.200
The journey takes 4 minutes

00:01:00.200 --> 00:01:09.200
When you leave the aircraft

00:01:09.200 --> 00:01:20.000
You will arrive at the satellite building

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:29.600
If your connecting gates are situated in the R,S,U or M sections

00:01:29.600 --> 00:01:38.400
These are located in the satellite building

00:01:38.400 --> 00:01:47.800
There is NO immigration control in the RSU section

00:01:47.800 --> 00:02:03.000
If Madrid is your final destination or if your connection is located in the HJK section

00:02:03.000 --> 00:02:12.000
You should take the train to the main building

00:02:12.000 --> 00:02:21.400
Business Plus, Gold, Platinum and Singular cardmember passangers...

00:02:21.400 --> 00:02:31.000
...will be able to use one of our VIP lounges to wait for their connection

00:02:31.000 --> 00:02:40.000
Please, pay attention to the instructions found in the airport

00:02:40.000 --> 00:02:50.000
Thank you for flying with Iberia and welcome to Madrid

00:02:50.000 --> 00:02:58.000
